    "rationale": "All 13 ASME V&V 40 credibility factors have been evaluated against MRL 5 requirements. Seven factors were formally assessed and all returned achieved levels below required levels. Six factors were flagged as not-assessed epistemic gaps. The overall credibility evidence package is accepted as a complete and transparent record of the current model maturity state; the model itself is not accepted for regulatory submission at this time pending resolution of identified gaps.",
